Comment: 1,0:00:11.12,0:00:13.55,JOJO5-op1-ch,,0,0,0,karaoke,梦想受到束缚
Comment: 1,0:00:14.08,0:00:16.26,JOJO5-op1-ch,,0,0,0,karaoke,沉重命运的意志
Comment: 1,0:00:16.58,0:00:19.68,JOJO5-op1-ch,,0,0,0,karaoke,如同被压迫直至覆灭
Comment: 1,0:00:21.61,0:00:24.05,JOJO5-op1-ch,,0,0,0,karaoke,前方已无处逃避
Comment: 1,0:00:24.35,0:00:26.64,JOJO5-op1-ch,,0,0,0,karaoke,唯有挣扎着前行
Comment: 1,0:00:27.00,0:00:30.82,JOJO5-op1-ch,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是我永远不会放弃
Comment: 1,0:00:30.87,0:00:36.79,JOJO5-op1-ch,,0,0,0,karaoke,瓦砾之中埋藏的
Comment: 1,0:00:36.93,0:00:41.85,JOJO5-op1-ch,,0,0,0,karaoke,希望的碎片
Comment: 1,0:00:42.63,0:00:47.41,JOJO5-op1-ch,,0,0,0,karaoke,用这双手 将它们找寻
Comment: 1,0:00:47.50,0:00:52.92,JOJO5-op1-ch,,0,0,0,karaoke,只为改变这世间
Comment: 1,0:00:55.61,0:00:58.28,JOJO5-op1-ch,,0,0,0,karaoke,Fighting Gold
Comment: 1,0:00:58.34,0:01:08.05,JOJO5-op1-ch,,0,0,0,karaoke,唯有相信自己的内心之人 终有一天方能闪耀
Comment: 1,0:01:08.69,0:01:16.94,JOJO5-op1-ch,,0,0,0,karaoke,燃烧全部生命 即便是神亦无畏惧 战斗永不停息
Comment: 1,0:01:17.18,0:01:21.66,JOJO5-op1-ch,,0,0,0,karaoke,不屈的魂灵
Comment: 1,0:01:24.40,0:01:27.08,JOJO5-op1-ch,,0,0,0,karaoke,Fighting Gold
